    dc:description "Figure 6. Ifrika pauculihirta (Benoit, 1957) comb. n. (A) Head, dorsal view. (B) Mesosoma, dorsal view. (C) Hypopygium, dorsal view. (D) Genitalia, dorsal view. (E) Genitalia, ventral view. (F) Harpe, gonostipes and volsella, inner view. (G) Harpe, gonostipes and volsella, outer view. (H) Aedeagus, lateral view. (I) Harpe, lateral view. Scale bars: A, B = 0.2 mm; C–I = 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10594466/files/figure.png" ;
